{"tid":194886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉向銀行職員送千元茶錢 中國商辯稱是付郵費","createTime":"2017-04-10T09:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T09:52:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20cb68a092acd21d7586a23ce0980bd6ba08d02d","tid":194886,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170410/large/1491816515_ec80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170410%2Flarge%2F1491816515_ec80.jpg&h=0b97c823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國五金商人來港欲為公司於匯豐銀行開立戶口，惟因帶不齊文件，涉在申請表及其他文件底下夾附一張「金牛」，向職員稱「請你喝茶，好好看着我的賬戶」，職員當場拒絕。商人離港後銷聲匿迹兩個多月，今年一月從羅湖再入境時被捕。他否認一項行賄罪，案件今開審，辯方指該1,000元是支付開設戶口郵寄及速遞文件的款項，不是賄款。<br />\n<br />\n男被告茹開順（51歲）是鳳發五金製品有限公司的唯一董事兼股東，控罪指他於去年11月3日在旺角向匯豐助理經理黎國仲提供1,000元，作為協助他為鳳發五金開立商業戶口的報酬。辯方亦投訴廉署調查人員恐嚇及誘使被告，聆訊明天繼續。  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170410/56546716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170410%2F56546716&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=4dec1790\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170410%2F56546716&h=3579d7e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170410/56546716</a>"},{"pid":"d48c272f1921a61db1c49cf89f62b25429f45b08","tid":194886,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59ba7d213094c96c1945c153b9e86458a8240c5","tid":194886,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:47:13.000Z","msg":"日日有唔知幾多人都私底下收左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdd9b3071c6318a17e7930bb1592204e3ed5ac2","tid":194886,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,